    <p class="col-start-3 row-start-5 pt-40 text-right italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...and i create scenography...</p>
    <p class="col-start-2 row-start-6 col-span-2 pt-10 text-center italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...and i get lost in golden light and pretty colors </p>
    <p class="col-start-3 row-start-6 pt-20 pl-4 italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">and disotrion and abstraction...</p>
    <p class="col-start-2 row-start-7 col-span-2 text-center italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...and i photograph...</p>
    <p class="col-start-3 row-start-7 col-span-2 pt-5 text-center italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...and make videos...</p>
    <p class="col-start-3 row-start-7 col-span-2 pt-10 text-center italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...and i edit them...</p>
    <p class="col-start-2 row-start-7 col-span-2 pt-30 text-center italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">...other than that, im a first year student at dmjx.</p>
    <p class="col-start-3 row-start-7 col-span-2 pt-35 italic text-indigo-300 font-serif">i study coded design.</p>
    
  </div>
</Layout>
